e17bd684-224c-4771-9820-0e23bfeb6103.title: Veronica
e17bd684-224c-4771-9820-0e23bfeb6103.text:
Can you please help me? I'm in a terrible spot of
trouble.

options.text: 遰 Aha, sounds like a quest. I'll help.
No, I'm looking for something to kill.

d81d3c42-f738-4eb4-b878-40c8c3a693b7.title: <player>
d81d3c42-f738-4eb4-b878-40c8c3a693b7.text: No, I'm looking for something to kill.

e4cebaa0-ed32-49e2-be19-322b858d1d6b.title: <player>
e4cebaa0-ed32-49e2-be19-322b858d1d6b.text: Aha, sounds like a quest. I'll help.

a3a56870-5a5c-4d2d-88b3-706d6059e128.title: Veronica
a3a56870-5a5c-4d2d-88b3-706d6059e128.text:
Yes yes, I suppose it is a quest. My fiance Ernest and
I came upon this house.

bba2739e-a0ef-45f7-9c8e-f94c7f8e26ed.title: Veronica
bba2739e-a0ef-45f7-9c8e-f94c7f8e26ed.text:
Seeing as we were a little lost Ernest decided to go in
and ask for directions.

8542cdd5-dbab-476c-99b7-f4e86663be9b.title: Veronica
8542cdd5-dbab-476c-99b7-f4e86663be9b.text:
That was an hour ago. That house looks spooky, can
you go and see if you can find him for me?

c31f537a-7bd4-4222-a57b-9f58893b1ca6.title: <player>
c31f537a-7bd4-4222-a57b-9f58893b1ca6.text: Ok, I'll see what I can do.

9278e449-01a9-490c-aa29-80fc905c119a.title: <player>
9278e449-01a9-490c-aa29-80fc905c119a.text: Thank you, thank you. I'm very grateful.

6494caec-5940-4ef8-9a65-bbdfc06fb129.title: Veronica
6494caec-5940-4ef8-9a65-bbdfc06fb129.text: Have you found my sweetheart yet?

9161ffa6-e4f2-41c2-b962-95c3f2cce559.title: Veronica
9161ffa6-e4f2-41c2-b962-95c3f2cce559.text: Have you found my sweetheart yet?

992dfb4e-ed9f-4cd4-89b7-961933d9f6e6.title: Veronica
992dfb4e-ed9f-4cd4-89b7-961933d9f6e6.text:
I know he's not exactly brave but I think you're being
a bit harsh.

b0f60f30-416b-4528-a332-312ff0a720ce.title: <player>
b0f60f30-416b-4528-a332-312ff0a720ce.text:
No no, he's been turned into an actual chicken by a
mad scientist.

4fe024e2-2124-4d75-9af8-d7a1ba79b4d7.title: Veronica
4fe024e2-2124-4d75-9af8-d7a1ba79b4d7.text: My poor darling, why must these things happen to us.

a37b8f13-a539-497a-a215-5fa3cfb3db5d.title: <player>
a37b8f13-a539-497a-a215-5fa3cfb3db5d.text: Well I'm doing my best to turn him back.

f341916d-4e67-4859-bf30-c8aec377e945.title: Veronica
f341916d-4e67-4859-bf30-c8aec377e945.text:
Well be quick, I'm sure being a chicken can't be good
for him.

5fded1dd-1b07-402c-aba6-f81e3e6bf54c.title: Veronica
5fded1dd-1b07-402c-aba6-f81e3e6bf54c.text:
Oh he went off to talk to some green warty guy. I'm
sure he'll be back soon.
